Title:	PUS1 PDF Measuring power usage	Procedure No.	PUS1-MOP-002	Risk Level:	Level 3	Frequency	Monthly	Owner:	PUS1 Facility Operations	Revision:	Rev 0.1	Equipment Affected:	N/A	Power source/ Breaker isolated	Power redundancy configuration	 
Description of Work 
This work is to check whether the branch circuit of the UPS distribution panel is actually used and whether the load is appropriate compared to the circuit breaker capacity in order to secure the customer's service stability.
